    "Song et al. [128] regard the abnormal part as the salient area of the image, and propose an effective saliency propagation algorithm for anomaly detection.",
    "Long et al. [129] investigate defect detection in a tactile image, which has obvious benefits for fabric structure defect detection in RGB images.",
