    "To detect defects in infrared thermal volumetric data, Hu et al. [130] propose a hybrid multi-dimensional space and temporal segmentation model.",
    "Ferguson et al. [131] use mask region-based CNN architecture to detect and segment defects in X-ray images simultaneously."
